Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:44.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 明明看起來那麼像一個部長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在也不是在意別人職位的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:48.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,儘量輕聲點穩當點…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:51.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這摩托真礙事兒…好窄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:53.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 課長叔叔你別推
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.74,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\shad6\fs150\bord6\c&H083FED&\3c&HDDDBE6&\4c&H27465A&\frz2.06\pos(914,830)}小知識環節
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.53,0:02:58.74,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad4\fs150\bord6\c&H083FED&\3c&HDDDBE6&\4c&H27465A&\frz2.06\pos(914,830)}小知識環節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,車輛級的排氣管稱為「Mufller」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:05.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在行車後會變得非常熱 可能會超過200度
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:05.20,shitang-zhengwen1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\shad3\fn@方正准圆_GBK\b1\frz270\c&H314FCD&\fs100\3c&H3C2E4D&\4c&HE1C9CA&\move(1540,283.333,1482,329.333)}小知識{\shad3\c&H4F0E04&}環節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:05.20,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\shad2\fs110\bord2\fn@方正大黑_GBK\frz269.8\c&H0200D2&\3c&H0E2889&\b0\4c&H0C42AC&\move(280,818,334,812)}危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:06.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果觸碰到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會出現這種聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:22.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事啊 小妹 叫得這麼大聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:29.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在找架打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 沒有沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:34.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像碰到了很熱的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:35.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒法說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:39.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞪著我還在笑 真是從容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 因為這是我的壞習慣…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 根據我們一族的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.84,0:03:47.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被找茬的時候不挑對手！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 腳浮起來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:02.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 快到打工的面試時間了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:11.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 趁他沒醒來趕緊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能會有人跟我一樣被燒傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只騎一會兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:21.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是重一點的自行車而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:23.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以動可以動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:35.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒！為什麼我老是不小心做錯事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.25,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完了完了完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:40.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就完全變成了我是壞人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 快醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:46.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.47,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底如果要查明原因的話明明是那個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:57.81,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲 醒來感覺怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:04.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…對我的摩托做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:07.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這制服肯定暴露了我是鮫島學園的人的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果逃跑 被發現也是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,地面太髒了我就試著把它墊在了地上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,橫也是死豎也是死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:19.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你這傢伙 知道自己在幹什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:20.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不如豁出去 在此決一勝負！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:22.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你沒有理解自己在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.42,0:05:26.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才為了不讓你死掉我可是手下留情了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.77,0:05:30.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你該不會以為自己只是因為疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.22,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然被普通的女人幹掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:34.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這人在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:37.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但這人最開始的時候笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:40.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你 到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:42.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:46.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次玩的遊戲果然還是很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的名字還是按以前的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.37,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs100\c&HD9D2CF&\b1\pos(892,144)}玩家姓名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:49.95,qianxu-huamian3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord2\fs100\c&HD9D2CF&\b1\pos(298,464)}血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:51.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(960,984)}Bloody Butterfly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.29,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 我從來沒聽過什麼血塗蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:56.37,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是在騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:06:00.29,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這也難怪 我跟你們在的舞台可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.25,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在你們用摩托玩過家家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:08.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是每晚都拿出槍桿在跟外國人對幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:09.01,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,槍桿…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,代理戰爭？黑社會的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh Don't kill me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這鬼話誰信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:16.52,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}聽好了 這是忠告
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:20.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下了這輛老土的摩托 馬上退出暴走族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是在浪費時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:25.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以為自己很神氣不斷跟外頭對幹 對幹 對幹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在追求些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:29.07,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那前方又有些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.37,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想過來這邊的世界嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:36.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊可是拿槍對幹到天亮 之後又開始後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻沒法回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:42.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,變成廢人的傢伙我也見得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要年紀輕輕就失禁穿尿布嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.04,0:06:47.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廢…廢人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:49.97,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是多管閒事罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別變成我這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:56.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是中下等 以普通為目標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:59.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,平穩是最好也是最難得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.81,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種荒誕無稽的話不知為什麼有點說服力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:08.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底難道你還有絲毫的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能拖著半毀壞的改造摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,堅稱自己是因為疏忽才被女人秒殺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.53,0:07:27.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我輸了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:31.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再跟你扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:35.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在最後 想讓你 聽一聽 我唯一的請求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到你的學校就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:42.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能陪我走完我的引退騎行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:47.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 好像把事情鬧大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:53.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝了 血塗蝶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:04.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血…血…血塗…血塗蝶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 剛才的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.04,0:08:11.72,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你 是我們學校的學生對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.01,0:08:14.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我 是留學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.93,0:08:17.81,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.93,qianxu-cut,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs120\xshad1\yshad1\bord3\c&HFFFFFF&\b0\3c&HFFFEFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\move(956,1220,956,1016,5,756)}千緒的{\fs150\bord6\c&HBFBFBF&}通學路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:26.19,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,700)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1443.2,875.6)}真奈菜和大腹和我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒 你不覺得最近情侶很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼一說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:33.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說的一樣 突然變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:36.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且都是高一的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要起名的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:39.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是「戀愛Noob」了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:43.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂Noob 就是表示「新手」「初學者」的遊戲用語
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:46.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱著對高中理想生活的嚮往的高一學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.73,0:08:48.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,常常不顧對方喜好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,容易趁著入學之初的勢頭開始與人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:50.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}戀愛 戀愛 戀愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:54.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 大多數這些戀愛Noob組成的情侶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會在被稱為「高中入學」的魔法逐漸消失下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在暑假以悲劇收場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}對不起 仔細看的話 你不是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:55.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.28,0:09:02.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直跟第一次上戰場的新手一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:05.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不去思考戰術和戰略 老實說真讓人看不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十二月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.34,0:09:11.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚯 說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:15.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高中時代跟異性交往的經驗有一次就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:19.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出了社會後 如果跟別人說高中時代有過兩個男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.00,0:09:21.29,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著不會讓人覺得有點放縱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.25,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高中生活接近尾聲時 戀愛會很礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:28.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以從活動多的大概高一的冬天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:29.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到高二的夏天為止
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受戀愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:37.09,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord0\c&H22334A&\pos(1350,168)}聖誕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:37.09,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord0\c&H22334A&\\pos(1350,212)}新年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:37.09,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord0\c&H22334A&\\pos(1368,262)}情人節
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:37.09,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs55\bord0\c&H22334A&\\pos(1350,310)}長假
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.17,0:09:37.09,qianxu-huamian2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs65\bord3\shad1\blur2\fad(500,0)\c&H0D0000&\3c&H8C8E80&\4c&H5E8C9E&\pos(166,396)}畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:34.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之後就調整好心態 專注於學習
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.83,0:09:37.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的中下等戀愛計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒 這張圖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:40.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在哪看過
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:42.01,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金槍魚大腹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:43.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:45.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,選到了戀愛最美味的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:46.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以上是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毫無戀愛經驗的兩人的蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:53.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說謊了我在逞強 我想跟大家一樣享受青春
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜 你太大聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管他的 反正大家都忙著跟對象說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.49,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.20,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:07.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那對情侶分開了3秒 物理上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.96,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,性格一如既往的差
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒的戀愛怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正實際上總顧著玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:18.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無言以對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:22.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前面的情侶 是細川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.12,0:10:25.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我認識 田徑部的名人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:28.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不突擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:31.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到了那種高次元的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,消失的就會是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:36.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這小市民的感覺 果然我們臭味相投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:40.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這兩人真是有模有樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然換成了帥哥美女想討厭都討厭不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手好像挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,師兄還問我要不要玩貝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:52.21,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀 手指好長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:53.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那比一比看看？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的在玩樂器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有沒有 我手沒那麼靈巧 肯定玩不來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.08,0:11:04.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挑戰一下嘛 我覺得樂器肯定適合你 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:04.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}真奈菜…「我」是在說誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:12.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出 出現了 絕招「車道很危險哦！！！」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊 嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你們停下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:15.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來如果兩人再來什麼喝同一杯水之類的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就再也沒辦法維持這個形態了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:31.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,健康的魅力情侶 往小巷的深處走了去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…色色的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼打擾了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別阻止我千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.76,0:11:41.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須得確認這裡面發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟名人的八卦不是很有價值嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.10,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想成為 話題的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,廢柴出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜 等一下 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.15,0:11:54.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果同班同學做出不純真的事的話就必須得制止他們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果被罵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:02.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人一起的話沒那麼痛苦 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:05.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種把自己行動的理由歸結到他人的錯上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好做好保險工作的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:11.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳千緒 這傢伙真的卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:12.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始潛入
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:19.25,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,位置情報 出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:22.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 兩個拐彎後是T字路口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:24.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個人好像還在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.76,qianxu-huamian1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\fs80\pos(944,902)}並沒有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在 超開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙才是最興奮那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把注意力集中在田徑上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:44.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以決定不和任何人交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了告白才把她帶過來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:50.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我喜歡跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:55.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 謝謝你能和我直說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:58.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,任性點說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:01.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和春木同學做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.01,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也還想讓你接著教我數學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:06.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:11.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種形式的話 也許我還能給你社團活動加油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.78,0:13:15.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那把你的朋友介紹給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.37,0:13:16.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友很多對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.55,0:13:19.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 也不是很在意我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕了告白就會變成這種清爽的場景嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:24.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不虧是細川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過最近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像和至今為止都不太一樣的類型的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:31.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成為朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是同班的三谷裳同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:35.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,戴著眼鏡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.36,0:13:37.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}偶爾會和她一起上學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:39.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}而且她又率直又可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學在說我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.01,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 我怎麼不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:48.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 你是細川同學的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:49.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是偶爾會一起上學…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個剛剛也聽到了 契機是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摔進垃圾堆裡就變成朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:04.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 你想拋棄我進入到那邊的圈子裡對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.74,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這樣嗎這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.15,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:12.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學 誇獎我…這個時間點…最糟…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:32.14,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒暴露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 接吻的時候 大家都是怎麼呼吸的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 嘴唇碰到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:40.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒碰到吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.50,0:14:44.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.91,0:14:49.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要裝得那麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:51.37,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:59.16,qianxu-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(900,700)\bord0.1\shad8\blur6\4c&H6E61CD&\pos(1498,878)}奴隸的蕩婦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.07,0:14:56.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早…早上好 千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.83,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三谷裳同學早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:15:00.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個組合怎麼回事 好稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.99,0:15:05.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼真奈菜會和細川同學在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:06.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:10.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在等你的時候細川同學路過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:11.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是名人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.00,0:15:14.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你是三谷裳同學的朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.56,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:17.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以一起等嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:18.43,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:20.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了 我是細川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:22.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}我是真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,意識到的時候就變成一起上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學真厲害 不愧是不怕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.91,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 真的這樣三個人一起走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:38.33,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 我有件事想問下細川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以哦 儘管問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.50,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學 是處女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.57,0:15:51.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 你都問了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼過分的質問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:58.18,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今為止沒有交往過所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.81,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我聽說你很受歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:04.73,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還被籃球部的春木同學告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事傳得這麼廣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,散布這件事的不就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們兩個人有嗎…這種經驗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人 沒有哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:21.41,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那親嘴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:28.63,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個的話 我就當兩個人的嘴唇應該沒有碰到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:29.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:30.76,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是中學的時候不過對象是大學生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:35.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中學的時候嗎 真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.93,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過契機是網絡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:41.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}在網上怎麼認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:43.27,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道 她一直瞞著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 這個感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像真奈菜突然遠去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:42.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}說起來有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}不過當時有個我熱衷的網絡對戰遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:46.90,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}然後在互發短信的期間…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:52.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三人聚集起來的話就是社會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.53,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這三人間 我是中心的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:17:00.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並確信著在這個社會裡我是有選擇權的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.70,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吶吶 今天要玩什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:05.37,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始是學問的時間哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.75,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.80,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正因為「學問能改變人格」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:10.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:11.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「女傑書簡」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是奧維德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(990,992)}Ovid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.97,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你還有文學的造詣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.12,0:17:22.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我淪落之前是專攻拉丁文學的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:23.98,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「變形記」是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：與「女傑書簡」同為奧維德作品
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我對於伊卡洛斯的插曲和納西索斯之後文學給予的影響…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}註：伊卡洛斯和納西索斯同為希臘神話人物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:31.61,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我不喜歡很難的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:33.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}葡萄好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.69,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎士比亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:36.78,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什麼竅門…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:45.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個小鬼 打算踩著我上去巴結細川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:46.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回想起來還是有伏筆的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.61,0:17:48.88,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不正是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:51.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,背叛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟敢…區區一個奴隸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.09,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像注意到了呢 千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.64,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 用起來還挺便利的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:03.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我就這樣利於和細川同學的友好關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,登上學校的上流圈子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我可能再也不會和你說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.63,0:18:11.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過至今為止真開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了 千緒 醬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:20.45,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野野村同學真厲害 真像大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 因為我懂這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點辛苦 不過我還是有看男人的眼光的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:29.00,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說 在那裡的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.71,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一生沒有將來性的普通職員的類型了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道自己看起來怎麼樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:38.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}果然社會地位是很低的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:37.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.43,0:18:38.93,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:43.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 是你朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:48.06,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位是學校附近公司的牛田先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:51.36,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雪是我跑步的師傅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:53.48,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交際圈太廣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:56.99,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在晚上跑步減肥的時候她過來搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.08,0:19:00.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你的跑步方法對膝蓋不是很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:03.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每次見面都會教我很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:05.08,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鞋子也是專用的果然不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:07.62,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那身打扮是細川同學推薦的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:09.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人 有點懷疑品味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.58,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}今天也是走路去公司嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.38,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}是啊 社長太胖的話就不能給社員做榜樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,社長？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.50,0:19:15.46,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在用濕毛巾擦下就換衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:18.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要不在公司搞個浴室好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.85,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 咦 咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是現充圈子的野野村同學誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:34.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思我這種下等的人突然和你搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:37.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.86,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭 表情超好看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:43.95,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思一不小心就看入迷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.01,0:19:47.24,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過果然上流圈子的人骨骼等級就是漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.79,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定整天被拉去聯誼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:49.66,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:51.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.42,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,野野村同學的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.92,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中學時代的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.34,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和大學生接吻的寶貴經驗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.00,0:19:58.13,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了後輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.51,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能告訴我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.26,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:02.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.19,0:20:05.30,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也沒和男生接吻過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:08.01,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是借鑑了時尚雜誌的體驗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.10,0:20:11.39,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:14.40,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對初中生出手的混蛋蘿莉控
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:16.57,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真奈菜的初吻對象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.65,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千緒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.11,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奈菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.82,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:30.12,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來 前面的大叔聽說是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:31.37,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:34.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算自己是大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.21,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果突然被細川同學搭話了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:40.67,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也會得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.86,0:20:42.84,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.89,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我好歹也是一名社長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.60,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:50.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像聽到了社長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能詢問下您工作的內容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.31,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 這個人對經濟方面感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有名片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:21:00.23,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,細川同學也有興趣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:05.41,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我說謊了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:07.32,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我只是一個普通職員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:09.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是為了裝逼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 我懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:14.16,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世間也有編造戀愛經歷的女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.02,0:21:16.21,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:20.17,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會在大賽的時候故意裝作身體不舒服的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:23.05,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牛田先生 最重要的事情只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:25.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跑步的距離不會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.56,0:21:29.68,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 低落的時候大家都跑起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 細川同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:36.44,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為細川同學只是想跑步而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:39.19,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.71,0:21:42.03,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過好像真的變得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:47.28,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己會被其他人怎麼看待 其實可能都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.46,0:21:56.04,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還想讓他們散開來跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:22:00.54,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過看他們表情挺不錯…中間那個大叔是誰啊！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:01.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,----ed----
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:33.55,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下回的千緒的通學路是由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:37.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「血塗蝶效應2」 和「卡巴迪4」兩部分組成
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:37.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(594,994)}Bloody Butterfly Effect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.53,0:23:37.77,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs60\an7}註：卡巴迪是一項印度和巴基斯坦青年男子的民間體育運動項目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.12,0:23:39.02,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:40.35,qianxu-zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最棒了
